                     <interp inst="t18431127-21-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing 4 1/2 yards of ribbon, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18431127-name-173" type="victimName">
