                  </hi>. (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took the prisoner—she told me the ribbon fell into her lap with her handkerchief, and she might have rolled it up and put it into her pocket unknown to her—4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. was found on her.</p>
